steps.name: User clicks on Women Tab
clicks on Quick View for the "Blouse"
changes the size of the dress to "M"
Adds it to the Cart
clicks on Continue shopping
User clicks on Quick View for the "Faded Short Sleeve T-shirts"
Adds it to the cart and closes the Quick View
User clicks on Cart
User should be directed to Cart summary page
User should see the selected dresses with correct sizes and prices in the cart
the total amount for the two dresses should be correct
Total amount to be paid should equals Total Products amount plus Shipping charges
User clicks on Proceed to Checkout
Confirms the address and agrees to the Terms of Service on Address and Shipping page
User clicks on Pay by Bank Wire on Payment page
clicks on I Confirm my order
Order confirmation page should be displayed
User Signs Out
